pping-stone'\npenetration pattern of APT attacks, which has confounded modeling approaches\nbased on normative rationality.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Nov 2018 15:00:10 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-16"}
